<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">    
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<style>
table {
  border-collapse: collapse;
  border-spacing: 0;
  width: 100%;
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
}

th, td {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 16px;
}

tr:nth-child(even) {
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h2>게시물 수는 : <%=noticeList.length%></h2>
<p>For zebra-striped tables, use the nth-child() selector and add a background-color to all even (or odd) table rows:</p>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>No</th>
    <th>제목</th>
    <th>작성자</th>
    <th>작성일</th>
    <th>조회수</th>
  </tr>
  <%for(var i=noticeList.length-1; i >= 0 ;i--){%>
  <%var notice = noticeList[i]; //배열에서 json하나 꺼내기%>
  <tr>
    <td><%=i+1%></td>
    <td>
      <a href="/notice/detail?notice_id=<%=notice.notice_id%>"><%=notice.title%></a>
    </td>
    <td><%=notice.writer%></td>
    <%var d = new Date(notice.regdate);%>
    <td>
      <%=lib.getZeroString(d.getFullYear())%>-<%=lib.getZeroString(d.getMonth()+1)%>-<%=lib.getZeroString(d.getDate())%>
    </td>
    <td><%=notice.hit%></td>
  </tr>
  <%}%>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="5">
      <button onclick="location.href='/regist_form.html'">글 등록</button>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
